              </a>
              <a class="iconRegister" href="#">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48"width="32px" height="32px"><path fill="#1778f2" d="M24 5A19 19 0 1 0 24 43A19 19 0 1 0 24 5Z"/><path fill="#ffffff" d="M26.572,29.036h4.917l0.772-4.995h-5.69v-2.73c0-2.075,0.678-3.915,2.619-3.915h3.119v-4.359c-0.548-0.074-1.707-0.236-3.897-0.236c-4.573,0-7.254,2.415-7.254,7.917v3.323h-4.701v4.995h4.701v13.729C22.089,42.905,23.032,43,24,43c0.875,0,1.729-0.08,2.572-0.194V29.036z"/></svg>
              </a>
